sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as MLflow SDK / Browser
    participant Gateway as ODH Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Auth as K8s Auth Plugin<br/>(in-process)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant WP as Workspace Provider<br/>(in-process)
    participant Server as MLflow Server<br/>5000/TCP HTTP
    participant DB as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: Experiment Tracking Request
        Client->>Gateway: POST /mlflow/api/2.0/mlflow/runs/create<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s SA)<br/>Header: X-MLFLOW-WORKSPACE
        Gateway->>Server: HTTP/5000 (cluster-internal)<br/>Bearer Token forwarded
        Server->>Auth: before_request hook
        Auth->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
        K8sAPI-->>Auth: allowed: true
        Auth->>WP: resolve workspace
        WP->>K8sAPI: Namespace list/watch<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
        K8sAPI-->>WP: namespace details
        WP-->>Auth: workspace context set
        Server->>DB: INSERT run record<br/>TCP/5432, DB credentials
        DB-->>Server: run_id
        Server->>S3: PUT artifact<br/>HTTPS/443, AWS credentials
        S3-->>Server: 200 OK
        Server-->>Gateway: JSON Response
        Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS Response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: AI Gateway LLM Invocation
        Client->>Gateway: POST /mlflow/gateway/{endpoint}/invocations<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s SA)
        Gateway->>Server: HTTP/5000
        Server->>Auth: before_request hook
        Auth->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS/443
        K8sAPI-->>Auth: allowed: true
        Server->>DB: SELECT provider config<br/>TCP/5432
        DB-->>Server: KEK-encrypted config
        Note over Server: Decrypt API key<br/>AES-256-GCM<br/>PBKDF2-HMAC-SHA256
        Server->>Server: Route to provider<br/>(traffic split / fallback)

        alt OpenAI Provider
            Server->>Gateway: POST api.openai.com/v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/443, API key
        else Anthropic Provider
            Server->>Gateway: POST api.anthropic.com/v1/messages<br/>HTTPS/443, API key
        end
        Gateway-->>Server: LLM Response
        Server-->>Gateway: JSON Response
        Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS Response
    end

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: OTLP Trace Ingestion
        Client->>Gateway: POST /mlflow/v1/traces<br/>Auth: Bearer Token<br/>Header: x-mlflow-experiment-id
        Gateway->>Server: HTTP/5000
        Server->>Auth: before_request hook
        Auth->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview<br/>experiment-scoped
        K8sAPI-->>Auth: allowed: true
        Server->>DB: INSERT trace spans<br/>TCP/5432
        DB-->>Server: trace_id
        Server->>S3: PUT trace artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443
        S3-->>Server: 200 OK
        Server-->>Gateway: 200 OK
        Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS 200
    end

    rect rgb(243, 229, 245)
        Note over Client,S3: Flow 4: Workspace Resolution
        Note over WP: Triggered on any API request
        WP->>K8sAPI: GET /api/v1/namespaces<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
        K8sAPI-->>WP: namespace list
        WP->>K8sAPI: GET mlflowconfigs.mlflow.kubeflow.org<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
        K8sAPI-->>WP: MLflowConfig (artifact overrides)
        Note over WP: Set workspace context<br/>on SQLAlchemy query scope
    end
